{"tid":1241918,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"股榮引KPMG報告：本港銀行內地風險大檢閱","createTime":"2019-06-19T01:18:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T03:09:40.000Z","uid":6604,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"cf6efbc76365168114273e41d1286107bda5df74","tid":1241918,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:18:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190617/large/1560748623_54b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190617%2Flarge%2F1560748623_54b3.jpg&h=03e5f3ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周末撰文題為《四萬億送中》，有網友想了解除東亞銀行（023）外，其他港銀於內地借貸及風險情況，找來一份畢馬威（KPMG)最新報告，會有點啟示。<br />\n<br />\n畢馬威上周發表《香港銀行業報告》，列出十間本港銀行內地風險敞口(exposure)，截至去年底止，金額最多為滙豐（8,420億元），其次是中銀及工銀亞洲，金額分別是6,270億及3,330億元，第四多就是東亞涉近三千億元。<br />\n<br />\n如果用內地風險敞口相比整體貸款（見表），比率最高分別是南洋商業（84%）、中信銀行國際（83%），及建銀亞洲（72%）及工銀亞洲(70%），除了南商母公司是信達外，其餘三間母企都是內地大型銀行集團。<br />\n<br />\n至於「純本地」銀行，內地風險敞口相比整體貸款，比率最高是東亞的59%，然後是中銀的49%，其他如滙豐、恒生、渣打及星展，比例大約二成多。<br />\n<br />\n港銀於內地風險因素，除了實際金額，還要考慮到審批過程及抵押品質素而定，管治水平良好、非家族式經營的港銀，審批內地貸款把關較佳，亦也解釋港銀股價強弱懸殊的關鍵。"},{"pid":"0d28ae71115c538a67a2c3134c71c6111845dc62","tid":1241918,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:20:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://home.kpmg/cn/en/home/news-media/press-releases/2019/06/hong-kong-banks-resilient-with-strong-growth-in-profitability-in-2018.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhome.kpmg%2Fcn%2Fen%2Fhome%2Fnews-media%2Fpress-releases%2F2019%2F06%2Fhong-kong-banks-resilient-with-strong-growth-in-profitability-in-2018.html&d=HhKtR2wUfRZLc9nBt5dK8NUqyFx8t7fe88%2BQEXu6%2F%2FM%3D&h=34d2af25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://home.kpmg/cn/en/home/news-media/press-releases/2019/06/hong-kong-banks-resilient-with-strong-growth-in-profitability-in-2018.html</a>"},{"pid":"88398bbde447a28ddd1c7bf9eb998f251b81f2c1","tid":1241918,"uid":38761,"like":6,"dislike":